y-sec-to-equity-funding-difficulties-were.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2017-02-07 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107114639/http://www.nytimes.com/1973/04/04/archives/insurance-fraud-charged-by-sec-to-equity-funding-difficulties-were.html |archivedate=November 7, 2017 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|Wolfson Weiner; Ratoff & Lapin\n|United States\n|Created fictitious insurance policies\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |Fund of Funds \u2013 [[Investors Overseas Service]]s\n|1973<ref>Anderson Firm Is Found Guilty of Fraud ''The New York Times'' November 5, 1981 {{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1981/11/05/business/anderson-firm-is-found-guilty-of-fraud.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2017-12-28 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107043105/http://www.nytimes.com/1981/11/05/business/anderson-firm-is-found-guilty-of-fraud.html |archivedate=November 7, 2017 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|[[Arthur Andersen]]\n|Canada\n|Mutual fund that inflated value of assets\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Lockheed Corporation]]\n|1976<ref>{{cite news | title = SCANDALS: Lockheed's Defiance: A Right to Bribe? | url = http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,917751-1,00.html | work = Time Magazine | date = August 18, 1975 | accessdate = July 3, 2016 | url-status = live | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160829122011/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,917751-1,00.html | archivedate = August 29, 2016 | df = mdy-all }}</ref>\n|\n|United States\n|\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Nugan Hand Bank]]\n|1980<ref>Owen, J. ''Sleight of Hand : The $25 million Nugan Hand Bank Scandal''; Balmain, Sydney, Australia: Colporteur Press, 1983. {{ISBN|0-86399-023-1}}</ref>\n|\n|Australia\n|\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[O.P.M. Leasing Services]]\n|1981<ref>A Close-Up Look At The Fraud That Ruined O.P.M. ''The New York Times'' May 1, 1983 {{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1983/05/01/business/a-close-up-look-at-the-fraud-that-ruined-opm.html?pagewanted=all |title=Arc