or, Bean & Whitaker]]\n|2009 <ref>{{cite news|author1=Floyd Norris|title=After Years of Red Flags, a Conviction|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/22/business/22norris.html|accessdate=20 December 2016|work=The New York Times|date=April 21, 2011|language=English|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221093416/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/22/business/22norris.html|archivedate=December 21, 2016|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|[[PricewaterhouseCoopers]]\n|United States\n|Fraudulent spending\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Monsanto]]\n|2009 to 2011 <ref>{{cite web|author1=Gretchen Morgenson|title=Monsanto Whistle-Blower: $22 Million Richer, but Not Satisfied|work=The New York Times|language=English}}</ref>\n|[[Deloitte]]\n|United States\n|Improper accounting for incentive rebates\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Kinross Gold]]\n|2010 <ref>Bayens v Kinross http://www.canlii.org/en/on/onsc/doc/2013/2013onsc6864/2013onsc6864.html?searchUrlHash=AAAAAQAGYmF5ZW5zAAAAAAE&resultIndex=4</ref>\n|[[KPMG]]\n|Canada\n|Overstated asset values\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Lehman Brothers]]\n|2010<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lehmanreport.jenner.com/ |title=Examiner's Report \u2013 Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc. Chapter 11 Proceedings |publisher=Lehmanreport.jenner.com |accessdate=November 1, 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111115193217/http://lehmanreport.jenner.com/ |archivedate=November 15, 2011 }}</ref>\n|[[Ernst & Young]]\n|United States\n|Failure to disclose [[Repo 105]] misclassified transactions to investors\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Amir-Mansour Aria]]\n|2011\n|IAO (Audit organization) and other Audit firms\n|Iran\n|Business loans without putting any collateral and financial system \n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Bank Saderat Iran]]\n|2011\n|IAO (Audit organization) and other Audit firms\n|Iran\n|Financial transactions among banks and getting a lot of business loans without putting any collateral\n|-\n! {{Rh}} |[[Sino-Forest Corporation]]\n|2011<ref>Hoffman, Andy (Jul. 15, 2011) [https://www.theglobea